  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318730/extras/c5d889ac22d6c959093c87730dc876e4.avif?t=1739628355\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《Anomalies Detective》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A psychological horror game with an episodic plot, thrillers and anomalies!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a fledgling paranormal detective. After accepting an unusual commission, your fate changes...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will try to explore secrets and find ways to escape in three major scenes: corridors at night, narrow alleys, and infinitely looping houses. Be careful, many abnormal things happened, as if some strange power wants to devour you...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Similar to the \"The Exit 8\" game, please find the abnormal things in each scene cycle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please pay attention to every detail in the scene, these anomalies are hidden in inconspicuous corners!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 3 chapters in the game, 3 independent Chinese scenes, more than 80 anomalies, some of which are very secret, waiting for your challenge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are multiple endings waiting for you to explore. When you find all the anomalies, you will unlock the deepest secrets...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Note: Some of the content of this game is driven by sound effects. It is recommended to wear headphones for the best experience.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay demonstration:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318730/extras/c1eb0b2e46645082587d58c96daea9d3.poster.avif?t=1739628355\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318730/extras/c1eb0b2e46645082587d58c96daea9d3.webm?t=1739628355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318730/extras/c1eb0b2e46645082587d58c96daea9d3.mp4?t=1739628355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the scene</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318730/extras/25a111081f39d4554f5e9a778b256e9c.poster.avif?t=1739628355\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318730/extras/25a111081f39d4554f5e9a778b256e9c.webm?t=1739628355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318730/extras/25a111081f39d4554f5e9a778b256e9c.mp4?t=1739628355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Found anomalies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318730/extras/4bc577266f6d5634ab69139e2c14a0ad.poster.avif?t=1739628355\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318730/extras/4bc577266f6d5634ab69139e2c14a0ad.webm?t=1739628355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318730/extras/4bc577266f6d5634ab69139e2c14a0ad.mp4?t=1739628355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supernatural crisis!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318730/extras/c5d889ac22d6c959093c87730dc876e4.avif?t=1739628355\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《Anomalies Detective》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A psychological horror game with an episodic plot, thrillers and anomalies!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a fledgling paranormal detective. After accepting an unusual commission, your fate changes...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will try to explore secrets and find ways to escape in three major scenes: corridors at night, narrow alleys, and infinitely looping houses. Be careful, many abnormal things happened, as if some strange power wants to devour you...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Similar to the \"The Exit 8\" game, please find the abnormal things in each scene cycle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please pay attention to every detail in the scene, these anomalies are hidden in inconspicuous corners!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 3 chapters in the game, 3 independent Chinese scenes, more than 80 anomalies, some of which are very secret, waiting for your challenge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are multiple endings waiting for you to explore. When you find all the anomalies, you will unlock the deepest secrets...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Note: Some of the content of this game is driven by sound effects. It is recommended to wear headphones for the best experience.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay demonstration:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318730/extras/c1eb0b2e46645082587d58c96daea9d3.poster.avif?t=1739628355\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://